	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This is old news, but <a href="http://hi.baidu.com/maxzhou88/blog/item/8e7abf2d96ecba30349bf78b.html" class="postlink">Maxzhou88 has released some source code</a> to several old "pirate" NES games made by Super Game, namely Boogerman and Pocohontas.  The download page is MSIE only.

		

		</td>
