	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />"FC System Develop Kit" needs NES Hardware platform to support it running. it is not a emulator,  it is only a debugger for FC game that playing with FC cartridge or using a RAM cart running NES file. no mapper problem.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


